Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然还是生气了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真以为要被扒层皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说「我要离家出走」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然说「做得到你就试试～」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是你一言我一语地就吵起来了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个浴巾呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个也睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有多渴望睡个好觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能一直离家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说也不能不去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话该你说么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃过一次就会越来越麻烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一天的话没啥影响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没事所以一天天逃下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来自己已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…这种事还真轮不到我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:00:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没白当家里蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算自己很难过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也尽考虑别人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧你!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样 只考虑别人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间还要更…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和雪集也曾经谈过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都被芽间束缚着…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她现在就在我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 没有相信芽间的事情啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…啊不…也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了咖喱牛肉哦 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,520元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱牛肉撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是你想那样的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来看日记…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的咖喱牛肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就知道芽间的愿望了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的芽间在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的芽间的心事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:23.52,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,257)}今天和大家一起玩了 很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:32.16,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(614,257)}今天和大家一起玩了 很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好随便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两句话除了「很好玩」「很高兴」 就没的不同了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 很不擅长写作文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这里稍微不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今天和大家一起玩时摔倒了 好痛」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这里也不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今天和大家一起去探望仁碳妈妈了」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探望…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 还真是经常去呢 大家结伴一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的妈妈一直在医院呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 给神仙写信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「请让仁碳的妈妈早日恢复健康」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么给他呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.74,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}注：龙势是一种烟花，像火箭一样升天，还有一些会内置降落伞等机关 吉田町每年10月的第二个周日会举办龙势祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大家决定一起做烟花了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我觉得好难」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不过我会加油」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想起来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「给烟花火箭里放封信 送给神仙吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 就是这个吧? 芽间的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候说要做 结果还是没成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了…我妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳什么的 我才不理他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜里吃饭的话要变猪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给你变猪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咸味拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加蛋花…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为阿健拉面没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想喂你点吃的 哄哄你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸快回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃快点儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不要跟来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来「啊～」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再做奇怪的事咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么逃学还穿制服?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没什么不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搭配都是我的自由吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花火药的购买和使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据「火药管理法」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要18岁以上有国家认证才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想钻空子的话 玩具烟花还有点可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也要执照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…果然没办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常想想 做烟花确实是需要认证的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 昨天整理房间的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是认真的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集大量烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆开取出火药全部集中到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放进厕纸芯里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会燃起来所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当然的吧 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 小孩好可怕!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得这是能行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前即使是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也觉得真能飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真以为会比龙势祭上看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞得更高更远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时觉得高中生什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去就像是很厉害的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无所不能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得那个时侯 真是什么都能做的到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先找找有没有什么可行的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本办不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算做了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一不是你说的芽间的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是徒劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟在你那儿的芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好确认过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能害怕向她本人确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间感觉似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(718,623)}Deja Vu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是跑前面的宿海和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目送他远去的可怜的雪集君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有说出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是那家伙说要到秘密基地集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…好像是芽间提出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被芽间打电话叫出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 她好像说要商量什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易想起来的 为什么不说?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为宿海在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原话是「瞒着宿海集合吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.00,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(382,251)}第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.00,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(277,422)}真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.00,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,390)}愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识会做的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我工作场所有个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在祭典的时候担任烟花师傅的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 仁太 你想做烟花吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和波波他们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那我就去拜托他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳仁碳仁碳仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.89,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}康达尔城出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 要我先跟他联系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事情到时再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就算是简单的也要用这么多的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是我不想给你们做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 如何了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20万?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我还没见过那么多钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没问题 总能搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和安鸣拼死地打工就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 别擅自决定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题嘛 互相帮助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 安鸣一周干足七天的话绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 我还什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来 打工!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是输入金额的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是二手货的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新品的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 在这里输入差价么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你一瞬间就学会了我一个月才掌握的技能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也花太多时间了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「荒银光临」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你就完全不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有打工的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校却请假么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那个不是没去上课的么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 怎么回事 他们两个有啥关系?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢 迎—光 临——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那家伙干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和以前一样没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我胶布 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿…海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接好了 安鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准这么叫!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花的事情他们好像是认真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 我们要不要也捐点钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要陪着宿海不务正业么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想管的话我也算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 可以出来一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝个茶什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要考试了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是年级第四呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年级第二的在胡说什么呢 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪你可是件很痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳回得太晚了 不良少年!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳绝对有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上很快就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.27,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上出门也很迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗专题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小狗是母的 那仁碳就绝对在做奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～茄子腌得真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗 小奥斯卡 母 7岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈巴狗啊 好可爱 身上的褶好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:46.42,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}小奥斯卡是点心店的招牌狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}它会跟小客人们打招呼 表示「欢迎光临」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:56.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}多亏了小奥斯卡 来光顾的客人多了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}老婆婆也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在签名簿上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:02.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}今天小奥斯卡也希望自己能够精神百倍 笑容满面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 仁太君退学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊 但是为什么那样说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 这问题很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前段时间 我看见他好像在打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太他 有没有跟父亲交待清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我们家尊重个人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都交给仁太他自己决定 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题 有问题 有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有问题!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 波波 我今天没有排班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长好像很喜欢那家伙的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上是和你一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 羊山的工地?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这活不会太重了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 要挣钱的话体力活是首选
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭烟花可是和钱一起飞走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望…芽间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多考虑一下自己的事情啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人不爽啊 你那态度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说雪集和鹤见子他们有没有跟你联络?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 时常会有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么在意仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 仁碳就仁碳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是那么叫的吗 有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫仁碳的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人 那边!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了 仁碳他 可是很帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在芽间不考虑自己的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仁碳…一直在帮芽间着想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小心脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便变动灯光的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风能吹动照明灯吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要有个限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈做的味道…很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 仁碳 上学很辛苦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说不定很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没想到比宅在家里要舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种「活着」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…「活着」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那个 不是说实际上的活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是到现在为止的我…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间也觉得 看到有种「活着」感觉的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也有种「活着」的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我把订金带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能请你先帮忙做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个啊 抱歉不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心和祭典的干事说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后干事就训了我一顿 说「居然去帮什么高中生」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是拼命在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁啊 那个干事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接去找他面谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…本间家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他姐 仁太他们 似乎为了你在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:25.78,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と夏の終わり　将来の夢
