Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:58.90,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}你叫住了我 说了声「一起回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:03.07,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}好兴奋 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.66,ed_cn_formal_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(200,0)}还记得那无数次的冒险
